query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mk k) NoMergeJoin(k mk mc) NoHashJoin(k mc mk cn) NoMergeJoin(cn k mc mk ci) NoMergeJoin(ci cn k mc mk an) NoHashJoin(an ci cn k mc mk n) NoMergeJoin(an ci cn k mc mk n t) */ select min(an.name) AS cool_actor_pseudonym,
min(t.title) AS series_named_after_char
from movie_keyword AS mk
inner join keyword AS k
on mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'character-name-in-title'
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
inner join company_name AS cn
on mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
inner join aka_name AS an
on an.person_id = ci.person_id
inner join name AS n
on an.person_id = n.id AND n.id = ci.person_id
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = t.id AND t.episode_nr < 8;
